nl.naturalis.lims2.oaipmh

Class SharedPostFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.naturalis.lims2.oaipmh.SharedPostFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAnnotatedDocumentPostFilter

    public class SharedPostFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAnnotatedDocumentPostFilter
    Post-filter shared by all geneious repositories. Will be applied before any repository-specific post-filters. This filters checks that
    • The document_xml column contains valid XML
    • The plugin_document_xml columns contains valid XML
    • The document_xml column contains at least one <note> element
    • The CRSCode_CRS note is present and has value "true"
    • The is_contig attribute in the plugin_document_xml column has value true in case of a DefaultAlignmentDocument
    Author:
    Ayco Holleman
